snippet.title: KINGDOM HEARTS INTEGRUM MASTERPIECE for Cloud – Nintendo Direct 2.9.2022 - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
From the first Kingdom Hearts to Kingdom Hearts III + Re Mind (DLC), experience all games from the renowned series separately or in one complete set all-in-one with the KINGDOM HEARTS INTEGRUM MASTERPIECE for Cloud.

Start your adventure today on Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/kingdom-hearts-integrum-masterpiece-for-cloud-switch/
